{#-
  Tooltip — hover/focus-triggered descriptive popup.

  Wrapper around a trigger (icon button, abbreviation, etc.) plus a
  `<span role="tooltip">` sibling. The CSS toggles tooltip visibility on
  `.theme-tooltip-wrap:hover` and `.theme-tooltip-wrap:focus-within`.
  The 400 ms show delay (anti-flash on accidental hover) is CSS
  `transition-delay`. The hide is instant (no delay-out — feels snappy).

  Esc dismiss requires JS — a minimal Stimulus controller `tooltip`
  (≈ 15 lines) stamps `data-state="dismissed"` on the wrapper when Esc
  fires inside it, suppressing the show until the user moves focus out
  and back in. Per [13-accessibility-baseline.md §2] "Tooltip — Hover or
  focus shows; Esc dismisses".

  Positioning is CSS-only (OQ-14 doctrine): 4 placements via
  `data-placement` (top default | bottom | start | end). The caller is
  responsible for ensuring the viewport edge doesn't clip the tooltip.
  JS-positioned tooltips with viewport-collision detection live in the
  Ring 2 Popover Compound (which can compose Tooltip).

  Parameters:
    label       (string, required)  — tooltip text content (already |trans'd)
    placement   (string, optional)  — top (default) | bottom | start | end
    htmlId      (string, optional)  — id of the tooltip span (used by trigger's
                                      aria-describedby). Auto-generated if absent.
    triggerId   (string, optional)  — id stamped on the trigger element (so
                                      external scripts can reference it)
    className   (string, optional)

  Block `trigger` (required):
    The trigger element — typically a <button> (icon-only or text), an <a>,
    or an <abbr>. The kit doesn't auto-stamp aria-describedby; the consumer
    MUST add `aria-describedby="{{ tooltipHtmlId }}"` to the trigger inside
    the block. The variable `tooltipHtmlId` is exposed to the block.
-#}

{%- set label      = label      | default(null) -%}
{%- set placement  = placement  | default('top') -%}
{%- set htmlId     = htmlId     | default('theme-tt-' ~ random()) -%}
{%- set triggerId  = triggerId  | default(null) -%}
{%- set className  = className  | default('') -%}

{%- set tooltipHtmlId = htmlId -%}

{%- set _classes = ['theme-tooltip-wrap'] -%}
{%- if className -%}{%- set _classes = _classes | merge([className]) -%}{%- endif -%}

<span
  class="{{ _classes | join(' ') }}"
  data-controller="tooltip"
  data-action="keydown.esc->tooltip#dismiss focusout->tooltip#reset"
  data-placement="{{ placement }}"
>
  {%- block trigger -%}{%- endblock -%}
  <span
    class="theme-tooltip"
    id="{{ htmlId }}"
    role="tooltip"
    data-placement="{{ placement }}"
  >{{ label }}</span>
</span>
